<P>
Photo, New Towers Reflect a Grand Design: With its interesting, wave-like 
design, the new Rio Vista Towers office building, near Friars Road and Stadium 
Way in Mission Valley, isn't just another one of those boxy reflective-glass 
office buildings that have sprouted up in cities across the country. DAVE 
GATLEY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
