UPPER BRACKET -- Saddleback (Sea View No. 1), bye; Palm Springs (Ivy No. 3) at 
Chaffey (Baseline No. 3); Fountain Valley (At-Large/Sunset No. 4) at Montebello 
(Whitmont No. 2); LB Jordan (Moore No. 3) at Antelope Valley (Golden No. 1); LB 
Wilson (At-Large/Moore No. 5) at St. Bernard (Camino Real No. 1); Central 
(At-Large/Desert Valleys No. 4) at Redlands (Citrus Belt No. 1); Santa Ana 
