CO; OFFICE BUILDINGS; BUSINESS; LOS ANGELES -- ECONOMY; LOS ANGELES -- 
DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT BUILDINGS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
