<P>
Who Do They Like Least? 
</P>
<P>
"Some people feel favorably toward one group and at the same time not so 
favorably toward another group. Generally speaking, do you think *Anglos feel 
least favorably toward Asians, or blacks, or Catholics, or Jews, or Latinos in 
Orange County ?" 
</P>
<P>
**Everyone surveyed was asked who do Anglos feel least favorably toward, who do 
Asians feel least favorably toward, who do blacks feel least favorably toward, 
etc. 
</P>
