<P>
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Moving Into Your Neighborhood 
</P>
<P>
"If there was a substantial increase in the number of *(minorities) moving into 
your neighborhood, do you think that would upset you personally at lot, or 
some, or only a little, or do you think a substantial increase in the number of 
(minorities) moving into your neighborhood wouldn't upset you at all?" 
</P>
<P>
"Well, what about your neighbors? If there was a substantial increase in the 
number of (minorities) moving into your neighborhood, do you think that would 
upset your neighbors at lot, or some, or only a little, or do you think a 
substantial increase in the number of (minorities) moving into your 
neighborhood wouldn't upset your neighbors at all?" 
</P>
<P>
* Question asked about blacks, Asians, Jews and Latinos. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
