<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY DIGEST: LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF; 
</P>
<P>
COUNTYWIDE; 
</P>
<P>
COMMUNICATION CLASS OFFERED FOR COUPLES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A communication workshop for couples will be held Wednesday at Golden West 
College. 
</P>
<P>
The program will include advice on increasing fulfillment and resolving issues 
harmoniously. It is open to couples who are dating, engaged or married. The 
presenters are a married couple, Bob and Joyce Simpson, who are also 
professional marriage counselors. 
</P>
<P>
The fee is $50 per person. Additional information can be obtained by calling 
the Community Services Office at Golden West College, 891-3991. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
